A worker polishes patterns on a pickle jar at Tiange Taoci Co in Southwest China's Chongqing on Saturday. There are more than 1,000 types of products made by the company including flowerpots and wine jars. They are welcome across the country in cities like Beijing and Shanghai, as well as East China's Shandong Province, and in foreign markets in Vietnam, Cambodia and Myanmar. The firm also offers jobs for 300 local farmers. Photo: IC  
